description: NOLA Ice is a mobile vending service that specializes in ORIGINAL New Orleans Sno-Balls! Have a special event? Call us! We come to you! Whether it's a birthday party, fundraiser, wedding, etc., an Original New Orleans Sno-Ball is a sure treat to get any party started! Call us today!It's so New Orleans to have a Sno-ball stand on just about every neighborhood block. So we are bringing this COOL New Orleans treat right to Birmingham, Alabama in our own unique way. Welcome to NOLA Ice – Birmingham's premier Original New Orleans Sno-ball company. If you're looking for a little New Orleans flavor, and would like to experience this unique tradition, stop by and we'll set you up with one of these cool, tasty treats!
name: NOLA Ice
